 e an exciting day at the museum full of engaging activities for the whole 
 community! On Saturday\, June 20\, 2026\, from 11 am to 4 pm\, the Tampa M
 useum of Art offers free admission to its lineup of fun activities and pro
 grams in its Vinik Family Education Center\, galleries\, and terrace. Prep
 are for a lively community celebration of this holiday\, also known as Fre
 edom Day\, with art-making activities\, live music and performances\, snow
  cones\, gallery activities\, and more! \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.g
