 , 2026  Location: Marti Maceo Cuban Club  Ybor City  Doors Open: 10PM  21 
 Over Event  WHAT TO EXPECT  High-energy DJ sets all night  Drink specials 
 to keep the vibes flowing  A perfect blend of music\, culture\, and celebr
 ation  Grown sexy atmosphere  come ready to show out  TICKET PRICING  20  
 Early Access (Online Only)  25  At the Door  Limited availability  secure 
 your spot now before prices go up!  WHY YOU NEED TO BE THERE This isnt jus
 t a party Its a Juneteenth celebration with purpose\, style\, and energy. 
