LOCATION:1617 N Franklin St Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:LOCATION: Rialto Theater Alleyway  1617 N Franklin St\, Tampa\
 , FL 33602 Rhythm and Hues is a quarterly program that will pop up from 6-
 9pm in the Rialto Theater Alleyway to service the Tampa Heights Neighborho
 od of Tampas Downtown. Immerse yourself in the vibrant world of creativity
  as you wander through this unique event. Witness the alleyway come to lif
 e with an explosion of color\, rhythm\, and artistic expression as talente
 d local artists showcase their mesmerizing work. \n\nPermalink: https://ww
 w.tampa.gov/node/188226
