SUMMARY:Central Park Jazz Jam
LOCATION:1213 N Central Ave Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Let the good times roll at Central Park Jazz Jam! This FREE co
 mmunity event celebrates the musical history of Downtown Tampas Central Pa
 rk neighborhood. Enjoy LIVE performances from local bands and musicians\, 
 along with family-friendly fun from the YMCA. Bring a chair (and your danc
 ing shoes!) as we fill the courtyard of the Tampa Black History Museum wit
 h encore-worthy music and community vibes. So lets get jazzy and swing it 
 like you mean it this jam is sure to end your evening on a high note! \n\n
 Permalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/177856
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/177856
